{
  "stem": "15694.9",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But never again, nobody knows about him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, he asked me if I wanted diet food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said, sounds good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Give me diet food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was semolina, sweet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It tasted good, but it didn't really fill us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I never asked for it again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But can you imagine in Auschwitz, a camp where a person doesn't count anything, it's like the music.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Semolina, there's something I can't even explain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It sounds ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It is ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I can't explain it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But we didn't ask for it again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then with a bigger sacrifice, we got ourselves a bigger [NON-ENGLISH], one that contained three liters of soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Now, in order to do that, Max Spira was afraid sort of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Could lose his job or worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He said, you do something for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I get up-- I had to get up five minutes early in the morning and look around if there were any food containers which were taken to the barracks each day, each night, left somewhere, and bring them back.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Well, it was obviously a job that wasn't needed, because in three weeks, I actually found one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was somehow-- I don't know how it was forgotten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But it was a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But from then on, we really got stronger again and filled out again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a neighbor of ours, we were eating in such a way that not many people could see us, because envy.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then a neighbor did see us, and he offered us a half a portion of bread for a smaller [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And for him, the contents-- it was the bottom of the container was worth much more.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
